2015-07-31	pwessel
	Added use of macros AX_LAPACK and AX_BLAS to find Lapack libs
	and allow compilation of sbas.

2015-07-26	pwessel
	Add search for location of boost libs/includes and an optional
	--with-boost-dir=<dir> option for unusual places.  Removed a
	bunch of unnecessary $(NETCDFHOME) references in Makefiles.

2015-01-27	pwessel
	Clean up makefiles, define M_PI for Linux.  Compiles on both
	Ubuntu and OS X.
	
2013-08-12	pwessel
	Added GMT5SAR wiki at SOEST for bug tracking etc. Added Kurt etc
	as members.

2013-04-05	pwessel
	Phase 1 of porting complete: Everything compiles and links.
	Next step is to actually test the code and fix mistakes.
	
2012-10-23	pwessel
	Migrated GMTSAR to GMT5SAR and started subversion repository.
